<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">所谓首异，是指被乘数和乘数的首位上的数字不相同；所谓尾1，即两个因数个位上的数字均是1。求个位数字是1的两个两位数的积时，可在两个十位数字积的后面，添写上它们的和（如果和大于或等于10，就要进位），再添写上1即是所求的积。可利用公式</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">(10a+1)(10b+1)=100×a×b+10×(a+b)+1</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">进行速算，其中a、b分别是被乘数、乘数十位上的数字。</Run>
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">61×71=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 61×71</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=100×6×7+10×(6+7)+1</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=4200+130+1</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=4330+1</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=4331</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>